{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:07:35.568318+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Based on the repository analysis, here is the **main Python dependency and service stack** for this FastAPI template:\n\n---\n\n## 🧩 Core Framework\n\n- **FastAPI** (with `all` extras) — web framework\n- **Uvicorn** — ASGI server\n\n## 🗄️ Database\n\n- **PostgreSQL** (via `docker-compose` service: `postgres:latest`)\n- **SQLAlchemy** — ORM with `as_declarative()` base model\n- **databases[postgresql]** — async DB driver integration\n- **asyncpg** — async PostgreSQL driver\n- **psycopg2** — synchronous PostgreSQL driver\n- **sqlalchemy-utils** — helpers (`database_exists`, `create_database`)\n- **Alembic** — database migrations (configured at `alembic/`)\n\n## 🔐 Authentication & Security\n\n- **python-jose[cryptography]** — JWT encoding/decoding (used with `HS256` algorithm)\n- **passlib[bcrypt]** — password hashing (`CryptContext` with bcrypt scheme)\n- **python-multipart** — form-data parsing (required by OAuth2PasswordBearer)\n- **fastapi.security.OAuth2PasswordBearer** — OAuth2 token authentication\n\n## 🔄 Redis Support\n\n- **aioredis** — async Redis client\n- **Redis service** (`redis:alpine`) declared in `docker-compose.yml`\n- Settings read from environment: `REDIS_HOST` and `REDIS_PORT`\n\n## 🧪 Testing\n\n- **pytest** — test framework\n\n## 🐳 Infrastructure\n\n- **Dockerfile** with Python 3.9\n- **docker-compose.yml** orchestration (web + postgres + redis)\n\n## 📁 Project Layout\n\n```\nmain.py          → FastAPI app entry, startup/shutdown hooks\napp/\n ├── base.py     → SQLAlchemy declarative Base with UUID primary key\n ├── db.py       → Database connection, engine, session factory\n ├── models.py   → Imports all models into metadata\n ├── routes.py   → Root router aggregator\n ├── schema.py   → Pydantic schemas\n ├── services.py → BaseService with CRUD helpers\n └── settings.py → Settings (DB, JWT, Redis, etc.)\nauth/\n ├── api.py      → Auth route prefix\n ├── models.py   → User model\n ├── schema.py   → Auth Pydantic schemas\n ├── services.py → JWT/hashing utilities + UserService\n └── exceptions.py\nalembic/         → Migration scripts\n```", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 578, "prompt_tokens": 10146, "total_tokens": 10724, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 17, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 9728}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 9728, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 418}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-flash", "system_fingerprint": "fp_8b330d02d0_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "f2078c27-c281-4b40-a0f5-b824fb4e0190", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3e9-8022-7323-8223-59daf1af8bfa-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 10146, "output_tokens": 578, "total_tokens": 10724, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 9728}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 17}}}}]}}}
